  <li>The <a href="http://prose.io/">Prose</a> content editor (built on Jekyll)</li>
  <li><a href="http://tinyurl.com/DHslack">Join the Digital Humanities Slack</a> (anyone can join, even if you have no DH experience) and check out the #publishing channel for discussions of Jekyll and other DH publishing platforms</li>
</ul>

